{"data": [{"id": "4743060", "title": "BK Technologies: Aggressive Margin Expansion Not Yet Fully Reflected", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fireman talking on radio\" data-id=\"157428923\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">racheldonahue/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment thesis</h2> <p>BK Technologies (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BKTI\" title=\"BK Technologies Corporation\">BKTI</a></span>) is a company that has had an extraordinary 2024 with a performance of 170% YTD; however, the growth prospects are just beginning because of its new line of BKR-9000 radios being rolled</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743060-bk-technologies-stock-aggressive-margin-expansion-not-yet-fully-reflected", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 20:21:39"}, {"id": "4743059", "title": "Taylor Morrison Home Corporation Stock Is Still On Sale", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A grey and white modern farmhouse.\" data-id=\"2027568389\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Joe Hendrickson</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In early September of this year, one company that I decided to revisit was <b>Taylor Morrison Home Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TMHC\" title=\"Taylor Morrison Home Corporation\">TMHC</a></span>). For those not familiar with the company, it operates as a homebuilder that <a href=\"https://s27.q4cdn.com/448041563/files/doc_earnings/2024/q3/presentation/TMHC-3Q24-Investor-Presentation-Final.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">focuses on</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743059-taylor-morrison-home-corporation-stock-is-still-on-sale", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 20:19:51"}, {"id": "4743065", "title": "Chart Of The Week: As Strategists Get Bold, Should You Fold?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A woman uses AI from her mobile phone to help investment decisions over lay with candlestick chart pattern , trend of using AI in daily life and investing concept\" data-id=\"2151571951\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"569px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Athitat Shinagowin/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>If you\u2019ve been following my work, you know I\u2019ve been advocating a bullish \u201c<a href=\"https://www.moneyshow.com/articles/marketminute-61271/the-moneyshow-market-minute-for-july-19-2023/?scode=059253\" rel=\"noopener noopener\">Be Bold</a>\u201d investing stance since the start of 2023. That means favoring offensive strategies and sectors over defensive ones, and generally staying</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151571951/image_2151571951.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743065-chart-of-the-week-as-strategists-get-bold-should-you-fold", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 19:55:00"}, {"id": "4743054", "title": "DNB Bank: Commission Income Boom Consolidated With Carnegie Acquisition", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"DNB bank office\" data-id=\"1250576664\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4598px\" height=\"3082px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Roland Magnusson</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>DNB Bank ASA</b> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DNBBF\" title=\"DNB Bank ASA\">OTCPK:DNBBF</a>) is an attractive banking pick that we've been covering for <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4686566-dnb-bank-solid-performance-duration-gap-being-solved\">quite a while</a>. The positives are <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4598428-dnb-bank-hits-the-middle-ground-of-rate-hike-benefits\">an ownership in Vipps</a>, which covers maybe around 5% of the market cap as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1250576664/image_1250576664.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743054-dnb-bank-commission-income-boom-consolidated-with-carnegie-acquisition", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 19:44:33"}, {"id": "4742951", "title": "GigaCloud: Buying Opportunity On Its Unjustified Meltdown", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Markets Continue Steep Dive On Fears Of Coronavirus Effect On Economy\" data-id=\"1203738110\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Scott Heins</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>GigaCloud: Emerging From Its Bear Market</h2> <p>GigaCloud Technology Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GCT\" title=\"GigaCloud Technology Inc.\">GCT</a></span>) investors have endured a highly challenging Q3, which saw the stock plummet from its March 2024 peak and then wipe out gains for 2024 before settling down</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203738110/image_1203738110.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742951-gigacloud-buying-opportunity-unjustified-meltdown", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 19:40:00"}, {"id": "4743050", "title": "BNY Mellon Research Growth Fund, Inc. Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Modern Stock Market Analysis Financial Growth in 3D Render.\" data-id=\"1560557977\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"977px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">lerbank</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <blockquote><p>As we move beyond the midpoint of the year, large-cap equities have demonstrated remarkable resilience.</p></blockquote> <h2>Performance Review</h2> <p>BNY Mellon Research Growth Fund (Class A at NAV) underperformed its benchmark, the Russell 1000\u00ae Growth Index (the \u201cIndex\u201d), during the third quarter of 2024. The industrials sector was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1560557977/image_1560557977.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743050-bny-mellon-research-growth-fund-inc-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 19:18:00"}, {"id": "4743049", "title": "Payoneer Global: Keep In The Basket As Payment Processors Expect Future Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Alipay, PayPal, Payoneer, Google pay, Wise, MoMo, GCash, Wechat and M-PESA app icon on screen.\" data-id=\"1499147711\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Robert Way/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>The Thesis</h2> <p>For the latest article in my continuing series on this platform, The Future Investor with Albert Anthony, I went searching for a stock in the financial sector trading for under $20, and I found it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499147711/image_1499147711.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743049-payoneer-global-stock-keep-in-basket-payment-processors-expect-future-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 19:04:23"}, {"id": "4743048", "title": "NewLake Capital Partners: Hold Out For This Cannabis-Driven REIT With Immense Potential", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close-up of natural pattern on cannabis leaf\" data-id=\"1403074050\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1015px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074